{"tid":407536,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"結婚生仔真係好似黑洞咁","createTime":"2017-09-20T13:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T14:41:09.000Z","uid":58316,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef31ba19f8e11298ee6c2ac68324b8d218bc983","tid":407536,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:23:34.000Z","msg":"屋企、社會無時無刻都想拉你入去<br />\n明明知道結婚生仔製造咁多悲劇<br />\n都好似着左魔咁，燈蛾撲火，自我毀滅<br />\n可能你仲細，十靚廿歲，覺得成家立室好美滿<br />\n但越近三十，你越係想逃走<br />\n甚至有時覺得連份三四萬既銀行工政府工都可以唔要<br />\n遠走他方，去撻冇人識你既地方，流浪又好，做泰山又好<br />\n有時睇戲，好嚮往d美國人揸住架車一路向西，係塊麥田中間，得佢一個<br />\n斷背山、不羈的天空、月黑高飛&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n諗下都爽"},{"pid":"e637aab7285151a19e3cf5f58d7a701007be363b","tid":407536,"uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"而家暫時冇工開<br />\n但返工個陣<br />\n最開心係放工係條街度鳩行<br />\n公司隔籬有間froyo<br />\n七八點得自己一個坐係間froyo店度食<br />\n好靜，好舒服<br />\n食完就行海皮<br />\n有時睇場戲<br />\n落pub飲啤酒唱k<br />\n夜晚既自己係最舒服"},{"pid":"0efd8a215b297728508c2247429f8a0178f1ba07","tid":407536,"uid":68736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"巴打比人催婚？"},{"pid":"2eff32c475129bb0f063db2edd4867ecd5407167","tid":407536,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:11:20.000Z","msg":"又形容得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaa5817b37c9cf809c68d22a1ae213faf21aaac","tid":407536,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9770343b1a3db9c513d8e289ea212d83cee8310","tid":407536,"uid":146548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"父母驚你老左冇人養，自己一個角落頭瀨屎瀨尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44537ff71138